		<h2>Background</h2>
		<div class="row cf">
			<div class="col3"></div>
			<div class="col7">
				<p>BuildCloud is a kick ass technology start-up based in Leeds. They had a vision to create a cloud based project managment tool for architects, which we transformed from a cool idea into a real product.</p>
