<section class="case-study__section--grey case-study--design">
	<div class="wrapper">
		<h2>Design</h2>
		<div class="row cf">
			<div class="col4">
				<div class="design-txt">
				<p>At its heart BuildCloud is about information &amp; communication so the design needed to put this to the fore. The interface was kept clean, clear and simple with a minimal core colour pallet. Subtle animations where used to provide greater context when interacting with the user interface.</p>
				</div>
